Interface HasLevel

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    HasExperience
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmmoCrate, ArcherMob, Arrow, CombatEntity, Crate, EliteMob, FastArrow, FountainOfHealth, HealthPack, Player, PlayerPet, PvpEntity, ResourceNode, SniperMob, Ticket, WarriorMob, WolfMob, Yralemounts, Zombiemounts

    public interface HasLevel
    Level is presented as a positive integer. Can only be increased and starts at 1. First class change at level 10, Second class change at level 25, maximum level is 99.
